This little phone book application with simple login and CRUD for contacts.
Using technologies:
- backbone 1.1.0
- bootstrap 3.0.3
- ejs
- jquery 1.10.2
- lo-dash 2.4.1
- firebase api

Into firebase use simple login with to possible users:
 login : admin@admin.com    pwd: 12345
 login : admin@new.com      pwd: 12345

 All of information saved into firebase data store.

 details:
 create 2 views -
 1) login form: user enters his login/pwd and if accepted, proceeds to the next view, otherwise show the error message.
 2) editable table (grid) with the phone book
 two columns - name and phone number.
 table is editable inline - i.e. you can add new row for a new person (double click the empty row), you can edit existing rows inline (double click the name or phone#), you can delete rows (show x button when the row is hovered).
 add phone number format validator (xxx-xxxx-xxxx) where x is a 0..9 digit
 add check for duplicate names.
